text: China's #Sinovac #COVID19 #vaccine has 50.7% efficacy and has proved to be effective against variants known as P1&P2 that are prevalent in Brazil. Moreover, Sinovac vaccine's efficacy rate can climb to 62.3% with an interval of more than 21 days between doses rather than 14 days. https://t.co/xVfr5iPWyS
